commentTextItems.html: cleans him up to finish the game

commentPostTextItems.html: So thats it for today, Canada put up a good fight especially chasing 303, most of the Canadians got in and then gave it away, Innings was lead by Cheema who scored a whirlwind 89 of 77 balls
Xavier Marshall is Man of the Match
This is Gary Grewal signing out, we will see you on Sunday for the finals

milestones.description: Marshall has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (12) in ODIs for WI, going past Greenidge's 8
Marshall has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (116) in an innings in ODIs for WI, going past Viv Richards's 114
Rizwan Cheema has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (76) in an innings in ODIs for CAN, going past John Davison's 68
Baidwan has conceded the most runs in an innings (77) in ODIs for CAN, going past Cummins's record of 74
This is the highest match aggregate (557) involving teams West Indies & Canada in ODIs
Marshall has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (12) in ODIs, going past Jayasuriya's 11
